title: Newly refurbished 2 bed apartment – Tisdall Place SE17
description:
Enter this apartment on the First floor to find two double bedrooms, a bathroom, small storage cupboard just off the hallway and an open plan kitchen to living area. The apartment has under floor heating in all rooms, large windows and high ceilings, making the space feel bright and airy.
The kitchen is of an Italian design containing all the latest Siemens mod cons and has been finished to an excellent standard. Here you will find an integrated microwave, dishwasher, washer/dryer (Hotpoint), induction hob with splash back, composite stone work surfaces, plenty of storage space and engineered wooden flooring. The lounge is a fantastic space with ample room for a sofa, dining table and chairs. Just off the living area are large doors, which open out to the private decked roof terrace, offering pleasant views of the London skyline and the perfect space for al fresco dining on those long summer days.
The bathroom is a white suite comprising porcelain tiles, large sink, W.C. and a rainforest shower over the bath.
Both bedrooms are carpeted and have ample space for double beds not to mention additional storage. The hallway has engineered wooden flooring, an entry phone and a storage cupboard, containing the meters.
